snippet.title: Looty Dungeon Announcement Trailer
snippet.description:
Looty Dungeon is an upcoming arcade-y endless dungeon crawler for iOS by Taco Illuminati. Play as dozens of characters with unique abilities and play-styles, battle monsters and bosses, and collect coins through multiple environments. 

Keep up with Taco Illuminati at http://twitter.com/illtaco
More information on Looty Dungeon can be found at http://lootydungeon.com/
